Explain in your own words and examples, what is Shell Scripting for DevOps. --> Shell scripting is a set of commands that we use to save the time for repetetive tasks , we often use shell scripting in order to automate the tasks and make our life easier.
What is #!/bin/bash? can we write #!/bin/sh as well? --> Yes both are same as we can write bash as sh.
